data.description: Adorable, 2BR 1BA brick home in a quiet neighborhood at Lake Brownwood.  Inviting, open living, dining and kitchen area makes for a comfortable living space and the large utility room has lots of storage.  The primary bedroom is massive with a huge walk in closet. The Jack and Jill bathroom is set up perfectly to accomodate the primary bedroom and the main living area. Sit on the covered patio to enjoy the secluded back yard which also includes a storage building and a chain link fence for your pets. The owners installed a new HVAC approximately 2 years ago, a new water heater and they are going to install a new roof as soon as possible. With all of the updates one can make the interior of the home their own with their own special touches.  Just minutes away from a boat ramp or swimming at the lake, shopping and dining, make this a great place to live. Don't wait too long or you will miss out on a great home!
